{"word":"G3076 - λυπέω - lypéō - loo-peh'-o - Cause grief","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λυπέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">lypéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">loo-peh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cause grief</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துக்கமடை, துக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to make sorrowful; to affect with sadness, to cause grief; to throw into sorroW"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3077 - λύπη - lýpē - loo'-pay/3077\">G3077</a>; to <i>distress</i>; reflexively or passively to <i>be sad:</i> - cause grief, grieve, be in heaviness, (be) sorrow (-ful), be (make) sorry.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G253/253\">G253</a>, <a href=\"#/G3076/3076\">G3076</a>, <a href=\"#/G3077/3077\">G3077</a>, <a href=\"#/G4036/4036\">G4036</a>, <a href=\"#/G4818/4818\">G4818</a>"}]}